\label{sec:data_and_meethods}
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

Our method for demonstrating
a consistent approach
for societal exergy analysis along
unified conversion chains (MCCs and ECCs)
is to elucidate mathematical expressions
and example calculations in full detail.
The mathematical expressions are shown in
Section~\ref{sec:exergy_of_materials} below.
We apply that approach to a unified
material and energy conversion chain,
following material from natural resource extraction
to pig iron production.
Data for the example MCC,
